[SPEAKER_00] slabiji proračun i sve ostalo.

590
00:41:26,559 --> 00:41:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] A ja mislim da tu ponovo Hrvatska

591
00:41:28,599 --> 00:41:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] može puno napraviti sama.

592
00:41:30,059 --> 00:41:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je fantastično pozicionirana.

593
00:41:31,920 --> 00:41:34,460
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo blizu našim emitivnim tržištima.

594
00:41:34,460 --> 00:41:35,519
[SPEAKER_00] Tu su ogromna tržišta

595
00:41:35,519 --> 00:41:37,400
[SPEAKER_00] Sjeverne Italije, Južne Njemačke, Austrije.

596
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,719
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala Bogu, ceste imamo.

597
00:41:38,719 --> 00:41:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ceste su tu, glavni alati su tu.

598
00:41:39,860 --> 00:41:41,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ceste smo malo skupo farbali.

599
00:41:41,659 --> 00:41:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što ja mislim da bi trebalo,

600
00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] da administracija treba jako puno raditi

601
00:41:45,500 --> 00:41:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] na komunikaciji, znači treba se ljude,

602
00:41:48,460 --> 00:41:51,440
[SPEAKER_00] da tak kažem, razbiti taj bavog cijepljenja, ne?

603
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:55,179
[SPEAKER_00] Cijepivo je tu i Hrvati bi trebali shvatiti,

604
00:41:55,179 --> 00:41:57,099
[SPEAKER_00] građani Republik Hrvatska bi trebali shvatiti

605
00:41:57,099 --> 00:41:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] da ukoliko mi danas možemo reći Evropi,

606
00:41:59,599 --> 00:42:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] gle, kod nas će se cijepiti 90% ljudi,

607
00:42:02,420 --> 00:42:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] onda će to Njemci imamo reći,

608
00:42:04,199 --> 00:42:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] čekaj, pa idem tamo, tamo su ljudi procijepili.

609
00:42:06,559 --> 00:42:08,139
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo nema opasnosti.

610
00:42:08,139 --> 00:42:09,239
[SPEAKER_00] Nego da idem u neku zemlju.

611
00:42:09,239 --> 00:42:10,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi su uzeli lijek.

612
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

613
00:42:10,980 --> 00:42:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi su se procijepili,

614
00:42:12,199 --> 00:42:13,820
[SPEAKER_00] na ovaj ili onaj način su stvorili

615
00:42:13,820 --> 00:42:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] tu prokuženost stanovništva

616
00:42:16,440 --> 00:42:19,739
[SPEAKER_00] i od domaćeg stanovništva mi neće prijetiti opasnost.

617
00:42:19,739 --> 00:42:21,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se eventualno cijepio sam u Njemačkoj,

618
00:42:21,780 --> 00:42:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] sve okej,

619
00:42:22,659 --> 00:42:24,239
[SPEAKER_00] idem uživati u tom jadrnu

620
00:42:24,239 --> 00:42:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] bez kojeg ne mogu,

621
00:42:25,079 --> 00:42:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] bez obirati da li sam iz Hanovera ili Berlina.

622
00:42:27,539 --> 00:42:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ključna stvar koju mi moramo gurati,

623
00:42:29,920 --> 00:42:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] mi to možemo.

624
00:42:30,579 --> 00:42:33,219
[SPEAKER_01] To je dakle bitka za cijepljenje sljedećeg godina.

625
00:42:33,219 --> 00:42:35,860
[SPEAKER_00] Pa izgleda je to barem

626
00:42:35,860 --> 00:42:38,699
[SPEAKER_00] na toj komunikacijskoj razini

627
00:42:38,699 --> 00:42:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] izvjetno važno.

628
00:42:40,539 --> 00:42:42,699
[SPEAKER_00] I ukoliko ta pandemija

629
00:42:42,699 --> 00:42:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] stane na vrijeme,

630
00:42:43,519 --> 00:42:45,179
[SPEAKER_00] nama je dovoljno da ona stane

631
00:42:45,179 --> 00:42:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] do kasnog proljeća,

632
00:42:46,860 --> 00:42:48,639
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi smo bliska destinacija,

633
00:42:48,639 --> 00:42:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] kod nas je čovjek može odlučiti

634
00:42:50,559 --> 00:42:51,519
[SPEAKER_00] doći zadnji čas.

635
00:42:51,599 --> 00:42:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što je isto važno za hrvatski turizam,

636
00:42:53,380 --> 00:42:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] ako mi ne da bože nešto nije dobro,

637
00:42:55,579 --> 00:42:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] sjednem u auto,

638
00:42:56,539 --> 00:42:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam za 4-5 sati ponovo doma

639
00:42:58,500 --> 00:43:00,739
[SPEAKER_00] u okrilju svojeg sjajnog Njemačkog

640
00:43:00,739 --> 00:43:01,800
[SPEAKER_00] ili kojeg već zdravstva.

641
00:43:01,800 --> 00:43:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] A ako sam odletio u neku dalju destinaciju,

642
00:43:04,920 --> 00:43:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] onda je tu puno više triki.

643
00:43:07,019 --> 00:43:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] Da, isto kako ja volim,

644
00:43:08,420 --> 00:43:09,820
[SPEAKER_01] ono, kad me stranici pitaju

645
00:43:09,820 --> 00:43:12,780
[SPEAKER_01] ako im mogu najkraće dočarati Hrvatsko,

646
00:43:12,780 --> 00:43:14,239
[SPEAKER_01] onda im pokušavamo objasniti

647
00:43:14,239 --> 00:43:16,300
[SPEAKER_01] da dožive Hrvatsku kao jedan grad.

648
00:43:16,300 --> 00:43:18,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo što mi zovemo gradovi,

649
00:43:19,039 --> 00:43:20,099
[SPEAKER_01] tu su ono kvartovi.

650
00:43:20,099 --> 00:43:22,880
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo kvart Dubrovnik, Split, Rijeku

651
00:43:22,880 --> 00:43:24,179
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje,

652
00:43:24,179 --> 00:43:26,119
[SPEAKER_01] a između su krasni parkovine,

653
00:43:26,119 --> 00:43:28,659
[SPEAKER_01] a sve je, ono, mislim,

654
00:43:28,659 --> 00:43:31,699
[SPEAKER_01] brže dođete evo iz ovog našeg studija

655
00:43:31,699 --> 00:43:33,659
[SPEAKER_01] u opati, u Narivu,

656
00:43:33,659 --> 00:43:35,400
[SPEAKER_01] nego s jednog kralom dona na drugi.

657
00:43:35,539 --> 00:43:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Točno, točno, da.

658
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, Slobodane, puno hvala

659
00:43:40,380 --> 00:43:42,119
[SPEAKER_01] kaj ste nam bili gost.

660
00:43:42,119 --> 00:43:43,079
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vama.

661
00:43:43,079 --> 00:43:44,860
[SPEAKER_01] Baš smo nekak, čini mi se,

662
00:43:44,860 --> 00:43:46,719
[SPEAKER_01] si lepo pospominjali.

663
00:43:46,719 --> 00:43:49,239
[SPEAKER_01] Želim vam sve najbolje u novoj godini.

664
00:43:49,239 --> 00:43:52,760
[SPEAKER_01] Imate li možda kako pitanje za nas?

665
00:43:52,760 --> 00:43:53,280
[SPEAKER_01] Nemate?

666
00:43:53,280 --> 00:43:55,719
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, ništa posebno.

667
00:43:55,800 --> 00:43:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] Drago mi je da radite,

668
00:43:57,619 --> 00:43:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] da imitirate.

669
00:43:58,460 --> 00:43:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] Nadam se da vam

670
00:43:59,440 --> 00:44:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] baza slušatelja raste.

671
00:44:01,400 --> 00:44:03,219
[SPEAKER_00] Raste, borimo se da naravno.

672
00:44:03,219 --> 00:44:04,440
[SPEAKER_00] I da će to ići dalje.

673
00:44:04,440 --> 00:44:06,239
[SPEAKER_00] Želim vam puno uspjeha u novoj godini.

674
00:44:06,239 --> 00:44:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] Sretan vam Božić,

675
00:44:07,079 --> 00:44:08,280
[SPEAKER_00] vama i slušateljima

676
00:44:08,280 --> 00:44:09,679
[SPEAKER_00] i samo napred.

677
00:44:09,679 --> 00:44:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] Što reći više,

678
00:44:11,659 --> 00:44:12,739
[SPEAKER_00] nego hvala.

679
00:44:12,739 --> 00:44:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] Slušajte i dalje Radio 808.

